 *                   representing the port.
 *    [consistency]  A consistency level specification. This is a [short]
 *                   representing a consistency level with the following
 *                   correspondance:
 *                     0x0000    ANY
 *                     0x0001    ONE
 *                     0x0002    TWO
 *                     0x0003    THREE
 *                     0x0004    QUORUM
 *                     0x0005    ALL
 *                     0x0006    LOCAL_QUORUM
 *                     0x0007    EACH_QUORUM
 */
